sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / DSP API
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Controller as workflow-controller<br/>9090/TCP metrics<br/>6060/TCP healthz
    participant StepPod as Workflow Step Pod
    participant ArgoExec as argoexec (sidecar)<br/>UID 2000
    participant S3 as S3-compatible Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant DB as PostgreSQL / MySQL<br/>5432/TCP or 3306/TCP

    Note over User,DB: Flow 1: Workflow Execution

    User->>K8s: Create Workflow CR<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8s-->>Controller: Watch event (informer)<br/>Watch stream TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8s: Create Step Pod<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8s-->>StepPod: Pod scheduled & started

    Note over ArgoExec,S3: Init Phase (download artifacts)
    ArgoExec->>S3: Download input artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Access key / IAM

    Note over StepPod: Main container executes workflow step

    Note over ArgoExec,S3: Wait Phase (upload artifacts)
    ArgoExec->>S3: Upload output artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Access key / IAM
    ArgoExec->>K8s: Patch pod annotations<br/>(WorkflowTaskResult CR)<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token

    Controller->>K8s: Update Workflow status<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token

    Note over Controller,DB: Flow 2: Workflow Archival (Optional)

    Controller->>DB: Archive workflow history<br/>TCP 5432/3306<br/>TLS configurable<br/>Auth: Username/password
    Controller->>K8s: Label workflow as archived<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token

    Note over Controller,K8s: Flow 3: CronWorkflow Scheduling

    Controller->>K8s: Create Workflow from<br/>CronWorkflow spec<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8s: Update CronWorkflow status<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
